/* Using the sequence function to create an editable table to capture data in an excel like format inside Canvas Apps */

Insert a ComboxBox
Insert a gallery 
Insert and Input Controls required into the gallery 
/*Change Item property into :*/  Sequence('Desired Number')
/*Change the Combox OnChange property to create a variable with the sequence function :*/ UpdateContext({Grid, Self.Selected.Value})
/* Change Gallery Item Property to the varibale */ Items = Grid
